{"sn1.13:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.13 ","sn1.13:0.2":"2. Nandanavagga ","sn1.13:0.3":"Natthiputtasamasutta ","sn1.13:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn1.13:1.2":"Ekamantam thita kho sa devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn1.13:2.1":"“Natthi puttasamam pemam, ","sn1.13:2.2":"natthi gosamitam dhanam; ","sn1.13:2.3":"Natthi suriyasama abha, ","sn1.13:2.4":"samuddaparama sara”ti. ","sn1.13:3.1":"“Natthi attasamam pemam, ","sn1.13:3.2":"natthi dhannasamam dhanam; ","sn1.13:3.3":"Natthi pannasama abha, ","sn1.13:3.4":"vutthi ve parama sara”ti. "}